title: Bike Carrier Roof - Thule FreeRide 532
description:
How to install the Thule FreeRide 532 bike rack on the roof of your car? This video will show you step by step how to do it. 

Thule FreeRide 532
The functional and easy to use bike carrier fulfilling all basic needs.

- Frame holder with quick-lock, fits most frame sizes up to 80 mm.
- Quick-release straps with wheel protection hold the wheels securely in place (adjustable for different wheel sizes).
- Lockable - bike to bike carrier, bike carrier to load carrier (locks included).
- The maximum allowed weight per bike is 17 kg.
- T-track adapters (20x20mm) are included for mounting on Thule WingBar Edge, Thule WingBar, Thule SlideBar, and Thule AeroBar.
- Fulfils the City Crash norm.

Learn more at www.thule.com
